data.description: Enjoy living in beautiful Bagley on one of its well maintained blocks. You will have great proximity to Marygrove, The Livernois Corridor, Palmer Park, Golf Course, Puritan development and shopping and services. This well kept brick home has a roof under 7 years old, properly maintained mechanicals, original hardwood floors, cove ceiling and medallion detail and built ins. Updated kitchen and baths that includes an oversized tub and stainless steel appliances. Large fenced in backyard, generous driveway, a two door garage that has a solid slab and newer roof. With four spacious bedrooms, a full bath on each floor and a huge partially finished basement this home is elegant, comfortable and convenient. It's ready for your personal style. Agent Verified: Not Haunted and No Monsters in Basement  Room sizes estimated. House sold AS IS outside of FHA/VA requirements.  BATVAI
